273
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:32,430
Okay. Good luck.

274
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:34,390
I'll help you take it to the office.

275
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,230
Okay, thank you.

276
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:37,870
Little brat.

277
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,950
He's so arrogant.

278
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:40,430
What a flatterer.

279
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,790
So what if he's the only son of the He family?

280
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:45,030
Jun, you already got the top grades.

281
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:46,110
